<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<I c="LootActions" i="action" m="interactions.utils.loot" n="loot_Cryptid_AskBirdaboutSelf" s="452091">
  <L n="loot_actions">
    <V t="notification_and_dialog">
      <U n="notification_and_dialog">
        <V n="dialog" t="notification">
          <U n="notification">
            <V n="icon" t="enabled">
              <V n="enabled" t="participant">
                <U n="participant">
                  <L n="participant_type">
                    <E>TargetSim</E>
                  </L>
                </U>
              </V>
            </V>
            <V n="text" t="variation">
              <U n="variation">
                <L n="variations">
                  <T>0x93CFDAB5<!--String: "Pardon my pinfeathers, you're asking about little old me? Why, I'm just the Peculiar Plumbird. I like to catch butterflies (I don't eat them like the smaller Plumbirds do—yuuuuuck!), go fishing, not think about Simstagram, and ask big questions like "why can't horses go on playground equipment?""--></T>
                  <T>0xDFD5F7F3<!--String: "You're probably wondering where I came from, right? I'm going to blow your little Sim mind right now; I came from the nest I'm often standing by. Why do you keep asking where my zipper is?!"--></T>
                  <T>0xB993B04<!--String: "I'm not interested in leaving my nest all that often but yes, I do like to see if I can get some toasted marshmallows at that 'Round the Fire Festival. Are you one of those weird Sims who like marshmallows to be burned, or are you normal and like them golden-toasty?"--></T>
                  <T>0x27183D96<!--String: "I am often asked if this is a paid position, which is a startling question to ask a giant bird. I don't know what I'd be paid for outside of merely existing. Can we be paid for merely existing? A Plumbird might like to have a little dosh on hand, so I'd be up for that."--></T>
                </L>
              </U>
            </V>
          </U>
        </V>
      </U>
    </V>
  </L>
</I>